title: It's More Than Numbers... It's Managing Emotions
description:
Domonique and Charlie break down MNF as usual with the Chiefs pulling off a comeback. Then, they get into the Panthers firing HC Matt Rhule, Chargers HC Brandon Staley and his most recent controversial play call, and Ashley Foxworth gives a few roses and thorns.
